<plot>Series 3 and 4 take the leap from serial drama to modern mythology, transporting our audience into the worlds of the living, the dead, and the in-between. Our guide through these worlds is the spirit of GP, a ghost who serves as the story's narrator. He relates Sifiso's story to us as a cautionary tale and with a message of hope: that it is never too late for us to make the right choice and make a change in our lives.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?210989</url></doc>
